// Fast-path with x == mod: AugLtMod evaluates false, normalize subtract zeroes x.
// y < mod stays as-is, sum = 0 + y = y, no overflow, sum < mod -> result = y.
// mod = 2^192 + 2^128 + 12345; x = mod; y = 2^192 + 7 (< mod since mod[2]=1, y[2]=0)
// (x + y) % mod = (mod + y) % mod = y
PUSH32 0x0000000000000001000000000000000100000000000000000000000000003039
PUSH32 0x0000000000000001000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000007
PUSH32 0x0000000000000001000000000000000100000000000000000000000000003039
ADDMOD
PUSH1 0x00
MSTORE
PUSH1 0x20
PUSH1 0x00
RETURN
